data.description: Gorgeous, like-new 4 bedroom & 3 full bath home nestled on a half acre in Carthage! You don't want to miss this stunning residence featuring a downstairs guest suite for privacy & convenience. With an open floor plan, natural light and functional living, this home has an abundance of features that every homeowner dreams of. The kitchen offers soft tail cabinets, under cabinet lighting, granite countertops, an oversized island for entertaining, pantry, stainless steel appliances and a breakfast nook. It also connects right to the formal dining room. Cozy up in the living area around the gas fireplace with views of the backyard. Upstairs you will find a loft, laundry room and 2 other bedrooms and a full bathroom. Don't forget the primary suite of your dreams!!! Boasting a sitting area, double sinks, luxury oversized tile shower, garden tub & Walk-in closet, this house doesn't miss a beat. Mudroom off epoxy coated garage. Back patio overlooks your large and leveled fenced backyard with views of soaring hardwoods and room for a pool.  Be sure to schedule your showing! Just minutes to downtown Southern Pines, Pinehurst. Zoned for Sandhills Farmlife, New Century Middle & Union Pines. 40 minutes to Ft Liberty & 25 min to Camp Mackall. Showings start January 18th.
